<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white> When I bought my Platinum Fire Wedding Ring i bought it for 500p. So i guess i might have got jipped because ow i hear that it has bee sold for like 400-435p the last 30days. BAAAHHH!</font></td></tr></table>
